<div class="recipes-recipe closed" data-udoingredients="liqueurs" data-id="amaretto-kick" id="amaretto-kick">
<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/amaretto-kick.png" alt="Amaretto Kick Cocktail Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Amaretto Kick</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>2 oz. amaretto</li><li>2 oz. sour mix</li><li>2 oz. orange juice</li><li>2 oz. Schweppes® Ginger Ale</li><li>1 maraschino cherry</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>In a cocktail shaker, add ice, then amaretto, sour mix, orange juice, and Schweppes Ginger Ale.</li><li>Stir mixture.</li><li>Strain into cocktail glass.</li><li>Garnish with cherry, and serve.</li></ul>
</div>
