<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/aperol-spritz.png" alt="Schweppes Sparkling Water Aperol Cocktail Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Aperol Spritz</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>2 oz. Schweppes® Lemon Lime Sparkling Water Beverage</li><li>2 oz. Aperol</li><li>2 oz. prosecco sparkling wine</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Combine ingredients and serve over ice.</li><li>Garnish with an orange.</li><li>Optional: Use Raspberry Lime or Orange Schweppes® Sparkling Water Beverage in place of Lemon Lime.</li></ul>
</div>
