<div class="recipes-recipe closed" data-udoingredients data-id="black-cherry-temple" id="black-cherry-temple">
<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/black-cherry-temple.png" alt="Black Cherry Temple Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Black Cherry Temple</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>1/2 cup ice</li><li>6 oz. (1/2 can) Schweppes® Black Cherry Sparkling Water Beverage</li><li>Rose’s® Grenadine</li><li>Cherries</li><li></li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Add 1/2 cup ice to a tall glass.</li><li>Pour 1/2 can Schweppes Black Cherry Sparkling Water Beverage over ice.</li><li>Add a splash of Rose’s Grenadine.</li><li>Garnish with a cherry, and serve.</li></ul>
</div>
