<div class="recipes-recipe closed" data-udoingredients="gin" data-id="bulldog" id="bulldog">
<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/bulldog.png" alt="BullDog Cocktail Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>BullDog</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>1.5 oz. gin</li><li>1 splash orange juice</li><li>Schweppes® Ginger Ale to fill</li><li>1 lemon wedge</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Fill a highball glass with ice.</li><li>Add gin, orange juice, and Schweppes Ginger Ale to top.</li><li>Garnish with lemon wedge, and serve.</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-push-5 col-md-7 share">
