<div class="recipes-recipe closed" data-udoingredients="gin vodka" data-id="buzzer" id="buzzer">
<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/buzzer.png" alt="Buzzer Cocktail Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Buzzer</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>1 oz. gin</li><li>1 oz. vodka</li><li>2 oz. grapefruit juice</li><li>2 oz. orange juice</li><li>Schweppes® Club Soda to fill</li><li>1 orange wedge</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Fill a collins glass with ice.</li><li>Add gin, vodka, grapefruit juice, orange juice, and Schweppes Club Soda to top.</li><li>Stir gently, garnish with an orange wedge, then serve.</li></ul>
</div>
