<div class="recipes-recipe closed" data-udoingredients data-id="creamy-colada-punch" id="creamy-colada-punch">
<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/creamy-colada-punch.png" alt="Creamy Colada Punch Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Creamy Colada Punch</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>24 oz. pineapple juice</li><li>8.5 oz. cream of coconut</li><li>12 oz. Schweppes® Ginger Ale</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>In a punch bowl, combine pineapple juice and cream of coconut.</li><li>Stir and chill for four hours.</li><li>Add Schweppes Ginger Ale, then serve. Serves 10.</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-push-5 col-md-7 share">
