<div class="recipes-recipe closed" data-udoingredients data-id="fantasy-island-punch" id="fantasy-island-punch">
<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/fantasy-island-punch.png" alt="Fantasy Island Punch Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Fantasy Island Punch</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>1 liter Schweppes® Club Soda</li><li>1.5 liters Hawaiian Punch®</li><li>4 liters 7UP®</li><li>2 liters orange juice</li><li>1 orange, sliced in rounds</li><li>1 bunch red grapes</li><li>1 quart strawberries</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>In a large punch bowl, combine Schweppes Club Soda, Hawaiian Punch, 7UP, and orange juice.</li><li>Stir mixture well.</li><li>Float orange slices, grapes, and strawberries.</li><li>Pour into rocks glasses, and serve. Serves 40.</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-push-5 col-md-7 share">
