<img src="/images/recipes/gin-and-tonic.png" alt="Gin and Tonic Cocktail Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Gin and Tonic</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>1.5 oz. dry gin</li><li>Schweppes® Tonic Water to fill</li><li>1 lime wedge</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Fill a collins glass with ice.</li><li>Add gin and Schweppes Tonic Water to top, then stir.</li><li>Garnish with a lime wedge and serve.</li></ul>
</div>
