<div class="recipes-recipe closed" data-udoingredients="whiskey" data-id="mint-julep" id="mint-julep">
<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/mint-julep.png" alt="Mint Julep Cocktail Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Mint Julep</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>1.5 oz. bourbon</li><li>1 tsp. sugar</li><li>1 glass crushed ice</li><li>1 splash Schweppes® Club Soda</li><li>10 mint leaves</li><li>Mint sprigs dipped in sugar</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>In a chilled collins glass, add 10 mint leaves, sugar, and Schweppes Club Soda.</li><li>Muddle the sugar and mint, then add crushed ice and bourbon.</li><li>Stir well, garnish with mint sprigs dipped in sugar, and serve.</li></ul>
</div>
