<div class="recipes-recipe closed" data-udoingredients data-id="mockmosa" id="mockmosa">
<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/mockmosa.png" alt="Mockmosa Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Mockmosa</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>1.5 oz. Schweppes® Original or Orange Sparkling Water Beverage</li><li>4 oz. orange juice</li><li>Sliced strawberry</li><li>Grenadine (optional)</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Pour 4 oz. orange juice into a champagne glass.</li><li>Add 1.5 oz. Schweppes Original or Orange Sparkling Water Beverage.</li><li>For a sunrise effect, add a splash of grenadine.</li><li>Garnish with a slice of strawberry on the rim, and serve.</li></ul>
</div>
