<img src="/images/recipes/moscow-mule.png" alt="Moscow Mule Cocktail Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Moscow Mule</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>1.5 oz. fresh-squeezed lime juice</li><li>2 oz. vodka</li><li>4 to 6 oz. Schweppes® Ginger Ale</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Squeeze lime juice into a collins glass, and drop the squeezed lime into the glass.</li><li>Add 2-3 ice cubes.</li><li>Pour in vodka.</li><li>Fill with Schweppes Ginger Ale.</li><li>Serve with a stirring rod.</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-push-5 col-md-7 share">
