<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Orange Fashioned</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>6 oz. (1/2 can) Schweppes Orange Sparkling Water Beverage</li><li>1 oz. orange juice</li><li>1 oz. Canadian whiskey</li><li>Bitters</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Add ice to a tumbler.</li><li>Pour 1/2 can Schweppes Orange Sparkling Water Beverage over ice.</li><li>Add 1 oz. orange juice.</li><li>Add 1 oz. Canadian whiskey.</li><li>Add a dash of bitters, and serve.</li></ul>
</div>
