<div class="recipes-recipe closed" data-udoingredients="tequila" data-id="paloma-wind-down" id="paloma-wind-down">
<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/paloma-wind-down.png" alt="Paloma Wind Down Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Paloma Wind Down</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>6 oz. (1/2 can) Schweppes® Pink Grapefruit Seltzer Water</li><li>1 oz. 100% agave tequila blanco</li><li>1 oz. grapefruit juice</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Add 1/2 cup ice to a tall glass.</li><li>Pour 1/2 can Schweppes Pink Grapefruit Seltzer Water over ice.</li><li>Add 1 oz. 100% agave tequila blanco.</li><li>Add 1 oz. grapefruit juice.</li><li>Stir mixture, and serve.</li></ul>
</div>
