<div class="recipes-recipe closed" data-udoingredients="brandy" data-id="red-sugar" id="red-sugar">
<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/red-sugar.png" alt="Red Sugar Cocktail Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Red Sugar</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>1.5 oz. brandy</li><li>.75 oz. lemon juice</li><li>1 tsp. grenadine</li><li>1 tsp. sugar</li><li>Schweppes® Club Soda to fill</li><li>1 orange slice</li><li>1 maraschino cherry</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Fill a cocktail shaker with ice, then add brandy, lemon juice, grenadine, and sugar.</li><li>Shake well, then strain into a collins glass filled with ice.</li><li>Add Schweppes Club Soda to top.</li><li>Garnish with orange slice and maraschino cherry, then serve.</li></ul>
</div>
