<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Seltzer &amp; Gin</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>1 oz. gin</li><li>6 oz. (1/2 can) Schweppes® Lemon Lime Sparkling Water Beverage</li><li>1 lemon</li><li>1 lime</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Muddle a slice of lemon and/or lime in the bottom of a tall glass.</li><li>Add ice.</li><li>Pour 1 oz. gin over ice.</li><li>Add 1/2 can Schweppes Lemon Lime Sparkling Water Beverage.</li><li>Garnish with a lemon or lime slice, and serve.</li></ul>
