<div class="recipes-recipe closed" data-udoingredients="vodka" data-id="spring-fling" id="spring-fling">
<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/spring-fling.png" alt="Spring Fling Cocktail Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Spring Fling</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>16 oz. vodka</li><li>16 oz. Schweppes® Club Soda</li><li>8 oz. lemon juice</li><li>11 oz. sugar</li><li>8 oz. fresh mint leaves (optional)</li><li>2 lemons</li><li>1 cucumber</li><li></li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Slice lemons and cucumbers into thin rounds.</li><li>In a large pitcher, combine vodka, Schweppes Club Soda, sugar, and lemon juice.</li><li>Stir until sugar is dissolved.</li><li>Add lemon and cucumber slices or fresh mint to mixture.</li><li>Chill, then serve over ice in old fashioned glasses.</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-push-5 col-md-7 share">
<h3>Share This Recipe</h3>
