<li><a href="https://pinterest.com/pin/create/link/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.schweppesus.com%2Frecipes%2Fspring-fling&media=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.schweppesus.com%2Fimages%2Frecipes%2Fspring-fling.png&description=Enjoy%20this%20bright-tasting%20cocktail%20for%20a%20quick%20boost%20in%20mood.%20Schweppes.%20Sparkling%20since%201783." data-social="pinterest" class="icon-pinterest share-link"></a></li>
