<div class="recipes-recipe closed" data-udoingredients="tequila liqueurs" data-id="sunrise-special" id="sunrise-special">
<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/sunrise-special.png" alt="Sunrise Special Cocktail Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Sunrise Special</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>1.25 oz. premium blanco tequila</li><li>.75 oz. crème de cassis</li><li>1 splash Schweppes® Tonic Water</li><li>Fresh lime</li><li>Orange wheel for garnish</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Fill a highball glass with ice.</li><li>Add tequila, fresh lime, and Schweppes Tonic Water.</li><li>Pour crème de cassis over the back of a spoon, down the side of the glass.</li><li>Garnish with an orange wheel, and serve with a straw.</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-push-5 col-md-7 share">
<h3>Share This Recipe</h3>
