<div class="recipes-recipe closed" data-udoingredients="tequila" data-id="tequila-schweppes-orange-seltzer" id="tequila-schweppes-orange-seltzer">
<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/tequila-schweppes-orange-seltzer.png" alt="Tequila &amp; Schweppes Orange Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Tequila &amp; Schweppes Orange</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>6 oz. (1/2 can) Schweppes® Orange Sparkling Water Beverage</li><li>1/2 oz. 100% agave tequila blanco</li><li>Orange juice</li><li>1 lime</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Salt the rim of a tall glass.</li><li>Add 1/2 cup ice.</li><li>Pour 1/2 can Schweppes Orange Sparkling Water Beverage over ice.</li><li>Add 1/2 oz. 100% agave tequila blanco.</li><li>Add a squeeze of fresh orange juice to top it off.</li><li>Garnish with a lime wedge, and serve.</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-push-5 col-md-7 share">
