<div class="recipes-recipe closed" data-udoingredients="vodka" data-id="vodka-cran-razz-in-the-city" id="vodka-cran-razz-in-the-city">
<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/vodka-cran-razz-in-the-city.png" alt="Vodka Cran-Razz in the City Recipe " />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Vodka Cran-Razz in the City</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>6 oz. (1/2 can) Schweppes® Raspberry Lime Sparkling Water Beverage</li><li>1 oz. vodka</li><li>1/2 oz. cranberry juice</li><li>Twist of lime peel</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Pour 1/2 can Schweppes Raspberry Sparkling Water Beverage into a martini glass.</li><li>Add 1 oz. vodka.</li><li>Add 1/2 oz. cranberry juice.</li><li>Garnish with a lime peel twist, and serve.</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-push-5 col-md-7 share">
