<div class="recipes-recipe closed" data-udoingredients="vodka" data-id="vodka-sonic" id="vodka-sonic">
<div class="container">
<span class="close"><img src="/images/updates/icon-close.png" /></span>
<div class="col-xs-4 feature-img">
<img src="/images/recipes/vodka-sonic.png" alt="Vodka Sonic Cocktail Recipe" />
</div>
<div class="col-xs-8 recipe">
<h2>Vodka Sonic</h2>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5 ingredients">
<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul><li>1.5 oz. vodka</li><li>1.5 oz. Schweppes® Club Soda</li><li>1.5 oz. Schweppes® Tonic Water</li><li>1 lime wedge</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-7 directions">
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ul><li>Fill a collins glass with ice, then add vodka.</li><li>Add equal parts Schweppes Club Soda and Schweppes Tonic Water to top.</li><li>Garnish with a lime wedge, and serve.</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-push-5 col-md-7 share">
